session.content:
Hello there! I'm glad you reached out. Can we start by discussing how you've been feeling lately? Are there any specific symptoms or concerns that have brought you to seek help today? I want to hear about everything, even if it seems minor or unrelated. This will help me understand your current health status better.

Also, if there is anything in particular that has been worrying you recently, please feel free to share that as well. My goal is to provide the best possible care and support for you, and open communication is crucial for that.

If it helps, I can take notes about our conversation so we can keep track of any changes or developments. How does that sound?

Please take your time to gather your thoughts before answering. I'm here to listen.

triage.reason: No red flags found; symptoms appear non-urgent.
